    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "This work improves the decision of which content pages should enter the editorial review queue first. An SEO specialist or content editor would use the ranked output, inspect the recommended pages, and decide whether to refresh, expand, protect, prune, or monitor each one. A false positive wastes editorial time and could lead to unnecessary changes to a page that is already performing adequately. A false negative may leave a declining or high-opportunity page unnoticed. The output will support human review rather than make automatic publishing decisions."
